('weather.ozweather', 'Oz Weather', 'Bossanova808', '0.4.3', 'Weather forecast data scraped from the Australian Bureau of Meteorology via WeatherZone - www.bom.gov.au and www.weatherzone.com.au.  For full features (e.g. radar) make sure you install the skin file you can find in the addon directory.  Contributed files for other skins welcome.', NULL, '2012-09-28', 'http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?tid=116905', NULL, NULL, NULL, 39393),
